            Today
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-medium text-flux-text-primary">Rest day</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-flux-text-secondary">
            Recovery is part of the program. Mobility welcome.
          </p>
        </div>
      )}

